00:05:07.279 --> 00:05:08.279
Huwag mahulog sa kanyang tukso.

00:05:09.519 --> 00:05:10.480
Isa akong chief kung tutuusin.

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:25.079
(Yung panaginip...)

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:27.480
Well,

00:05:27.480 --> 00:05:28.319
